@startuml
actor Student
    participant "React Frontend" as React
    participant MerchandiseController
    participant MerchandiseRepository
    participant OrderController
    participant PlaceOrderCommand
    participant OrderRepository
    participant OrderEventEmitter
    participant NotificationObserver
    participant NotificationRepository
    participant MongoDB

    Student->React: Navigate to Catalog page
    React->MerchandiseController: GET /api/merchandise?page=1
    MerchandiseController->MerchandiseRepository: findAll({isActive:true})
    MerchandiseRepository->MongoDB: find(merchandise)
    MongoDB-->MerchandiseRepository: [items]
    MerchandiseRepository-->MerchandiseController: Merchandise[]
    MerchandiseController-->React: 200 OK + paginated items

    Student->React: Select item (size auto-filled from saved profile)
    React->React: Read sizeProfile from auth context
    Student->React: Click proceed to Payment
    React->React: Render Payment Page
    Student->React: Complete simulated payment
    note over React: 1.5s simulated processing delay
    React->OrderController: POST /api/orders {items, totalAmount}
    OrderController->PlaceOrderCommand: new PlaceOrderCommand(orderData)
    PlaceOrderCommand->OrderRepository: create(orderData)
    OrderRepository->MongoDB: insertOne(orders)
    MongoDB-->OrderRepository: Order document
    OrderRepository-->PlaceOrderCommand: Order
    PlaceOrderCommand->OrderEventEmitter: emitOrderPlaced(order)
    OrderEventEmitter->NotificationObserver: handleOrderPlaced(order)
    NotificationObserver->NotificationRepository: create({userId, type:"order_placed", message})
    NotificationRepository->MongoDB: insertOne(notifications)
    PlaceOrderCommand-->OrderController: success
    OrderController-->React: 201 Created + order details
    React-->Student: Order confirmation screen

@enduml
